#: ../../N/nontrivial.rst:5
msgid "nontrivial"
msgstr "nontrivial"

#: ../../N/nontrivial.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../N/nontrivial.rst:9
msgid ""
"Requiring real thought or significant computing power. Often used as an "
"understated way of saying that a problem is quite difficult or impractical, "
"or even entirely unsolvable (\"Proving P=NP is nontrivial\"). The preferred "
"emphatic form is decidedly nontrivial. See :ref:`trivial`\\, "
":ref:`uninteresting`\\, :ref:`interesting`\\."
msgstr ""
"真の思考や相当な計算能力を要する。問題がかなり難しい、あるいは非現実的、あるいはまったく解決不能でさえあること(「P=NPの証明はnontrivialだ」)を控えめに言うやり方としてしばしば使われる。好まれる強調形はdecidedly"
" nontrivialである。\\ :ref:`trivial`\\ 、\\ :ref:`uninteresting`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`interesting`\\ を参照。"
